org.apache.beam.it.neo4j

Class Neo4jResourceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.it.testcontainers.TestContainerResourceManager<Neo4jContainer<?>>
      • org.apache.beam.it.neo4j.Neo4jResourceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.beam.it.common.ResourceManager

    public class Neo4jResourceManager
extends TestContainerResourceManager<Neo4jContainer<?>>
implements org.apache.beam.it.common.ResourceManager
    Client for managing Neo4j resources.

    The database name is formed using testId. The database name will be "{testId}-{ISO8601 time, microsecond precision}", with additional formatting.

    The class is thread-safe.
